  "texts": [
    "Hence, both α and β i remain fixed.",
    "Consequently, the Pcc is solely influenced by x i and x, with no dependency on y i and y.",
    "If the distribution of computation results is relatively concentrated, the difference x ix becomes smaller.",
    "This results in an elevation of the Pcc and a reduction of the MSE.",
    "For instance, considering the calculation results obtained using BERT, which fall within the range of 0.75-0.99, the MSEs for SICK are notably minute, while for other corpora, they approach 0.2558."
  ]
